title: Prof BOF Reviews “Attack Trigger”… The Skill Flopped, The Players Didn’t | Showtime De Jong & James
description:
Prof BOF reviews the new special skill Attack Trigger in eFootball 26, testing it on two Showtime cards: Reece James and Frenkie de Jong. On paper, Attack Trigger promises smarter runs and improved attacking movement — but does it actually make a difference in real gameplay?

In this video, I break down:

✅ What Attack Trigger is supposed to do
✅ In-game testing with Reece James & De Jong
✅ Movement patterns and attacking behavior
✅ Where the skill underperforms
✅ Why the players themselves still shine
✅ Final verdict: Is Attack Trigger worth it?

Even though the skill didn’t impress me, both cards delivered strong performances overall. If you’re considering these Showtime players or curious about Attack Trigger, this review gives you the full picture.

God invaded my heart with this sound.
He invaded time with that which is timeless.
God superimposed the natural state with glory and to birth this  supernatural sound . 

Friends,

As we approach the end of the age, it is pertinent that all flesh align with our Master and Lord, Jesus Christ, in one accord from family to family , generation to generation and across nations around the world.

Water does a cleansing work, but fire! fire is jealous.
It takes all of you and leaves nothing but  that which is eternal .

No wonder Jesus, the greatest, baptizes not with water, but with fire.

Fire removes that which can escape  water.

Its purifying power is irreversible, nothing escapes it, and it separates the holy from the profane.

Fire leaves only what is eternal as it refines, bringing out value and a new form from that precious stone . 

In the last days, there will be shakings; only that which is of God will stand.

The King of Glory rides on this sound, bringing light, igniting the will of sons through holy heat. 

I pray that as this sound reaches you, you allow yourself burn  till true  worship is ignited in you and all flesh that comes in contact with you.  

Spread the word for EVERYTHING IS ABOUT TO CATCH 🔥 🔥🔥
